You can build whatever decorators you need for your specific authorization scheme. Call `current_app.login_manager.unauthorized()` to enter the authentication flow.

```python
def admin_required(f):
    @functools.wraps(f)
    def wrapped_view(**kwargs):
        if not current_user_is_admin():
            return current_app.login_manager.unauthorized()
        return f(**kwargs)
    return wrapped_view
```

